Released versions
=================

1.1.0

  * adds dsettings command
  * supports environment variables in dcloud configs
  * adds otel to profiles
  * replaces remote_user by trace context
  * monitors cloud resources more efficiently
  * separates creation of AMI into dcloud-ami
  * migrates base AMI to Amazon Linux 2023

